short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Open the Google search results link in a new tab.
short.ja: Google検索結果のリンクを新しいタブで開きます。

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Only sites on a different domain will open in a new tab.
This is useful when you want to open all the sites you want to see first.
